Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.10,2:02:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是你想象中那么好的男人
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.17,2:02:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是一个好主人 更不是一个好人
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.46,2:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定配不上你
Dialogue: 0,2:02:51.42,2:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但要是
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.20,2:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在我还是
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.35,2:03:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱着你
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.66,2:03:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.69,2:03:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}待在我身边 薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.91,2:03:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
